des: This skill is the second part of the Digital Assistant Research skill that will be used to collect data for a research project conducted by the Pratt Institute team. The study aims to investigate user preferences for Alexa personality and is approved by IRB (#9142019-AD-IL). The skill is a supplement to an instruction form that is used by volunteer participants recruited from the Pratt Institute community.
